# Cursor Rules Location

Always follow these rules when creating cursor rule files

1. Only use `.mdc` for the file extension
2. Always place rule files in `PROJECT_ROOT/.cursor/rules/`
3. Use kebab case for filenames
4. Make filenames descriptive of the rule's purpose